        <item>
            <title>日本買房還是泰國買房？優缺點、貸款條件一張表就懂</title>
            <description>&lt;figure class=&quot;caas-figure&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-figure-with-pb&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-img-container&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;caas-img has-preview&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://media.zenfs.com/en/twtech.applealmond.com/da4e5d4fcb73bb4c146393c82629e6fe&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;隨著台灣&lt;a href=&quot;https://applealmondhome.com/posts/tag/%E6%88%BF%E8%B2%B8&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:房貸;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;房貸&lt;/a&gt;環境越來越嚴苛，不少投資人將資金投向海外市場，特別集中在&lt;a href=&quot;https://applealmondhome.com/posts/tag/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:日本;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;日本&lt;/a&gt;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://applealmondhome.com/posts/tag/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:泰國;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;泰國&lt;/a&gt;。對於在日本置產的台灣人來説不受限貸影響；相對之下，泰國的房貸條件較為嚴格，讓投資熱度逐漸消退。本文將針對台灣人在日本與泰國投資房地產的貸款條件進行比較，。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;想了解</description>
            <link>https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%90%88%E4%BD%B5%E4%BA%9E%E5%A4%AA-iphone-16%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82-%E9%81%A0%E5%82%B3q3%E6%B7%A8%E5%88%A9%E7%99%BB8%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-ai%E9%9B%B2%E7%AB%AF%E5%AD%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%8A%E6%AB%83-084600530.html</link>
